            "initiative": 7,
            "movement": 5
        },
        "cards": "cards/dodger.json", 
		"advice": "*Dodger hated delving through the dusty tomes. It was always the more practical aspect of dark magic that fascinated her, so when a daemon offered to complete her training by bypassing the boring formalities, it took a mirror for her to realize that there was fine print in that contract.*\n---\n- Your main weakness is your low defense. Keep this in mind when leveling up.\n- You are stronger when there are many empty minion spawn points in the battle zone, which can be achieved by defeating minions or displacing them through other means.\n- Play your silver card on turns when you expect enemy heroes to attack minions."
    },
